100%26fm%3Djpg%26q%3D90&cd=2023-03-14T03%3A26%3A24 241w,/_gatsby/image/6a5dc72cddadeb9a931b3ce65fec0106/af96df0bf46078320a35c0b8af2a7637/Magento-install.jpg?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebguru.dev%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2FMagento-install.jpg&a=w%3D482%26h%3D200%26fm%3Djpg%26q%3D90&cd=2023-03-14T03%3A26%3A24 482w,/_gatsby/image/6a5dc72cddadeb9a931b3ce65fec0106/378195405942174e5a12574007a483cf/Magento-install.jpg?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebguru.dev%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2FMagento-install.jpg&a=w%3D963%26h%3D400%26fm%3Djpg%26q%3D90&cd=2023-03-14T03%3A26%3A24 963w\",\"sizes\":\"(min-width: 963px) 963px, 100vw\"}},\"layout\":\"constrained\",\"width\":963,\"height\":400},\"alt\":\"How to Install Magento 2 on Mac 06\",\"className\":\"wp-image-1393 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\",\"data-wp-inline-image\":\"5\"}</script><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Magento Setup</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Once all previous steps in the Setup Wizard have been completed, click &#8216;Install Now&#8217;.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Upon successful completion, a message reading &#8216;Success&#8217; will be displayed to indicate a successful installation.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>(7) Verifying the Results</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Check the results by navigating to both the front end and back end of the website.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In conclusion, this guide has provided a detailed step-by-step process for <a href=\"/how-to-install-magento-2-4-using-composer/\">installing Magento 2.4 Using Composer</a> on a Mac OSX system. Starting with the installation of MAMP as the local web development solution for your Mac, you can set up Composer and download the M2 package. This guide will walk you through the steps to <strong><em>install Magento 2 on Mac</em></strong>, including the readiness check, database creation, web configuration, store customization, admin account setup, and final installation. To ensure a smooth and successful Magento 2 installation on your Mac using Composer, it is important to follow these steps and take the necessary precautions. Don&#8217;t forget to verify the results by checking both the front end and back end of your website. By following this guide, you can easily learn <strong><em>how to install Magento 2 on Mac</em></strong> and <strong><em>Magento 2 Install on Mac</em></strong> using Composer on a Mac OSX system.</p>\n<div class='sfsi_Sicons sfsi_Sicons_position_left' style='float: none; vertical-align: middle; text-align:left'><div style='margin:0px 8px 0px 0px; line-height: 24px'><span>Please follow and like us:</span></div><div class='sfsi_socialwpr'><div class='sf_fb_share sf_icon' style='text-align:left;vertical-align: middle;'><a  target='_blank' rel='noopener' href='https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=/how-to-install-magento-2-on-mac-a-complete-guide-using-apache-nginx-mysql-mariadb-and-php-7-x/' style='display:inline-block;'><img class='sfsi_wicon'  data-pin-nopin='true' alt='fb-share-icon' title='Facebook Share' src='https://webguru.dev/wp-content/plugins/ultimate-social-media-icons/images/share_icons/fb_icons/en_US.svg' /></a></div><div class='sf_twiter sf_icon' style='display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;margin-left: 7px;'>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a target='_blank' rel='noopener' href='https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=How+to+Install+Magento+2+on+Mac+https%3A%2F%2Fwebguru.dev%2Fhow-to-install-magento-2-on-mac-a-complete-guide-using-apache-nginx-mysql-mariadb-and-php-7-x%2F'style='display:inline-block' >\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img data-pin-nopin= true class='sfsi_wicon' src='https://webguru.dev/wp-content/plugins/ultimate-social-media-icons/images/share_icons/Twitter_Tweet/en_US_Tweet.svg' alt='Tweet' title='Tweet' >\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div></div></div><div class=\"saboxplugin-wrap\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\" itemscope itemprop=\"author\"><div class=\"saboxplugin-tab\"><div class=\"saboxplugin-gravatar\"><div data-gatsby-image-wrapper=\"\" styl